pokedexEntries.gold: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It always licks its paws because they are soaked with honey.
pokedexEntries.silver: Before food becomes scarce in wintertime, its habit is to hoard food in many hidden locations.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It always licks honey. Its palm tastes sweet because of all the honey it has absorbed.
pokedexEntries.ruby: This Pokémon likes to lick its palms that are sweetened by being soaked in honey. Teddiursa concocts its own honey by blending fruits and pollen collected by Beedrill.
